snippet.title: Viking Village Gameplay
snippet.description:
Viking Village is a fun classic RTS game. Defend your village from Pirates, Barbarians and nightly invasion of evil Knights!
Google Play link: https://goo.gl/j64FB8
iOS link: https://goo.gl/NZyeDc

Create and defend your village. Control units directly! No timers, energy system, coins and loot crates!

Website: http://www.limitless.online
